dc_title_s: The Daily telegraph war map no. 9 [pictorial relief map of European Turkey, the Dardanelles, the Sea of Marmara, and the Bosporus]
dc_description_s: Shows railroads, roads, and forts; does not show campaigns.; Relief shown pictorially and by spot heights.; Includes glossary and 5 inset maps.|76 x 101 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:350,000|General Map Collection
